        "ggQUtpalAyq_text": "<p>\"This blanket made my home feel like a five-star suite...\"</p>",
        "ggZez4m9rL6_text": "<p>I always thought I had nice blankets—until this one arrived. The moment I unwrapped it, I was stunned by its silk-like softness and elegant drape. One evening under this luxurious fleece, and I found myself lighting candles, pouring a glass of wine, and reveling in an experience that felt straight out of a high-end hotel.</p>",
        "ggYD-6DWJ30_text": "<p>-Alisa G.</p>",
        "ggQX2x4aXlp_childItem_0": "<p>Verified Customer</p>"
      }
    },
